{"tid":2017754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】大戰DC Fever美國騙徒","createTime":"2020-05-15T08:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T09:01:40.000Z","uid":280922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"76f51d2b046b55b79472215a8f485a255c11e2ff","tid":2017754,"uid":280922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>結論</ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 錢一日未到户口，千祈唔好寄貨<br />\n2. 出其不意，唔好跟騙徒劇本走<br />\n3.￼ 諗辦法嘥晒佢啲時間（例如填下form）￼</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>正文</ins></strong><br />\n小弟第一次起DC Fever放售MacBook Air，有個騙徒留低咗美國電話號碼+1(321)285-9701，叫小弟WhatsApp佢<br />\n名同相應該係假，註冊咗WhatsApp Business Account (Shopping &amp; Retail)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ezgPFFW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FezgPFFW.jpg&h=98d0e028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n￼￼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pM3ObNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpM3ObNA.jpg&h=4502313e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n騙徒一開始同意俾咗錢先，小弟再寄貨。小弟不虞有詐￼，俾佢嘥9晒啲時間影相、quote運費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n￼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dECvp81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdECvp81.jpg&h=1bc0df53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直到小弟收到兩封假銀行email（要小弟寄咗貨先會放筆錢俾小弟），先知道俾人搵笨￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dELdnVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdELdnVQ.jpg&h=e2e376fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/koia9AQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkoia9AQ.jpg&h=5ffa5df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n￼<br />\n真嗰間銀行噚日確認：兩封email都係假<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htgDy2z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtgDy2z.jpg&h=9d271761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢叫小弟寄去嘅地址只係一間偏遠停車場（Estes Express Lines運輸公司），收件人個名（Suzanne Anthony）應該都係假￼￼<br />\n地址：2202 Newton Rd Albany GA 31701<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ofuYy2J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FofuYy2J.jpg&h=2c3d07e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n￼<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>小弟唔撚下佢當然唔甘心</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 小弟扮傻仔，信晒佢銀行封email￼<br />\n2. 佢想小弟用FedEx，小弟就用順豐（鬼佬唔撚識中文￼￼）<br />\n3. 佢好心急打過幾次俾小弟，小弟偏偏唔聽￼<br />\n4. 小弟呃佢要install微信先至可以追蹤包裹￼￼￼<br />\n5. ￼￼本身想呃佢填多份海關嘅表格（不過失敗咗￼￼）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvgoK9J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvgoK9J.jpg&h=36d88ee8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zwqwT22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzwqwT22.jpg&h=b547b757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1f6oK9G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1f6oK9G.jpg&h=32d9a4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pW5EiuH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpW5EiuH.jpg&h=8d03b275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n￼<br />\n俾小弟玩左成日，佢終於發現順豐單據（求其上網揾）￼上面個電話係亂填￼<br />\n互相踢爆之後，小弟就block咗佢￼￼<br />\n寄咗email去當地警局報案，不過冇回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dc7e4fcc5870cc3c34fe19b0519aa8736192b0","tid":2017754,"uid":23951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"鬼佬又會識上肥花？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034652b5abba216741d1d176c620a41835b8a7d2","tid":2017754,"uid":358540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:01:01.000Z","msg":"樓主識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab8a988c2c4447fb7334f5a03b8d1464de20d91","tid":2017754,"uid":280922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2dc7e4fcc5870cc3c34fe19b0519aa8736192b0","tid":2017754,"uid":23951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"鬼佬又會識上肥花？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:01:40.000Z","msg":"明明冇英文版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vsta9Ju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVsta9Ju.png&h=7d28604b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}